7\t## 流程图\n     8\t\n     9\t### 发送消息\n    10\t\n    11\t```mermaid\n    
12\tsequenceDiagram\n    13\t    participant C1 as User A (Flutter)\n    14\t   
participant WS as Socket.io Gateway\n    15\t    participant S as ImService\n   
