e:send\n    21\t    WS->>S: handleSendMessage\n    22\t    S->>DB: verify conver
sation membership\n    23\t    S->>DB: insert message\n    24\t    S->>R: incr u
nread_count:B:convId\n    25\t    WS->>C2: event: message:receive\n    26\t    a
lt B offline\n    27\t        S->>Push: send push notification\n    28\t    end\
n    29\t```\n    30\t\n    31\t### 已读回执\n    32\t\n    33\t```mermaid\n    
34\tsequenceDiagram\n    35\t    participant C2 as User B\n    36\t    participa
nt WS as Socket.io Gateway\n    37\t    participant S as ImService\n    38\t    
participant DB as MySQL\n    39\t    participant R as Redis\n    40\t    partici
