age_id)\n    43\t    WS->>S: handleReadReceipt\n    44\t    S->>DB: update parti
cipant last_read_message_id\n    45\t    S->>R: reset unread_count:B:convId\n   
46\t    WS->>C1: event: message:read_receipt\n    47\t```\n    48\t\n    49\t## 
